definition.value: A monoterpenoid indole alkaloid with cytotoxic activity.
A member of the class of furans that is furan substituted by propionyl and methyl groups at positions 2 and 5, respectively. It is a flavouring agent found in sesame seed oil and coffee.
A glycosyloxyflavone that is apigenin substituted by a beta-D-glucopyranosyl moiety at position 7 via a glycosidic linkage.
